9174,"uid":31150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>條防水膠條甩左，整返要幾錢？兩隻窗都想換</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你預都要幾百一隻，因為太少窗同都係要拆窗</blockquote><br />\n咁換玻璃，一隻窗幾錢到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得，幫你問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89224160fc3090e7f6d7d40e815bcd6450813733","tid":49174,"uid":18432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"讀個課程考埋牌，part time接job咁做，有冇得諗"},{"pid":"df90d3ec9942da7d1888e00ca0dce4e9918a3517","tid":49174,"uid":28220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T01:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我廁所有隻窗 280mm x 1000mm, 要幾錢？要包埋搭棚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泥水窗定套窗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔明啊巴打，本來係玻璃百葉"},{"pid":"c7366c2d822b8fb41b656a9b353bb1a48aef7214","tid":49174,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:04:47.000Z","msg":"政府個驗窗計劃,應該點搵一個好公司,唔想比人搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋啲師傅會唔會話要換嘢而收多錢咁?<br />\n<br />\n窗台擺滿嘢搬開都幾麻煩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c51d65ba52c0fba9629c36ea2e00b256c91d9d","tid":49174,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我廁所有隻窗 280mm x 1000mm, 要幾錢？要包埋搭棚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泥水窗定套窗？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔明啊巴打，本來係玻璃百葉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n套窗 指唔折舊框直接套個新上去<br />\n好處唔駛搭棚，快同平但隻窗會細左。<br />\n<br />\n泥水指傳統做法搭棚折舊框，做防水，裝新窗。"},{"pid":"fb20d98291b2adb2524e0bf0b8bfd0c21933ef2e","tid":49174,"uid":68208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀個課程考埋牌，part time接job咁做，有冇得諗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d難<br />\n因為你無人幫你搵單"},{"pid":"f3e9edcea7